## Key System Components
1. **CRM System** - Customer and candidate relationship management
2. **Job Ingestion System** - Automated job posting and management
3. **Career Site & Landing Page** - Public-facing candidate interface
4. **Chatbot System** - AI-powered user support
5. **Intergroup CRM Sync** - Bi-directional data synchronization
6. **Mojo + Easy Apply** - Enhanced application process

## Technology Stack
- **Frontend:** React.js, Next.js, TypeScript
- **Backend:** Spring Boot (Java), FastAPI (Python), Express.js (Node.js)
- **Databases:** PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis
- **Cloud:** AWS/Azure hybrid approach
- **Containerization:** Docker, Kubernetes

## Implementation Phases
- **Phase 1:** Foundation & Core Systems (8-10 weeks)
- **Phase 2:** Integration & Synchronization (6-8 weeks)
- **Phase 3:** User Experience & Advanced Features (8-10 weeks)
- **Phase 4:** Testing & Optimization (4-6 weeks)

